column5: Looking to hear sucsess stories from Wine Lake Resort

We catch plenty of walleye every time we go. Within 30 minutes we caught a 27.5 and 29.5 inch walleye. Last time someone in camp caught a 31 inch walleye. We catch a lot of lake trout early in the shallows. Great camp if you like to be secluded and nobody around you. Scott
Heard the first week somebody pulled out a 34" 14lb walleye and a 34lb laker.
